<p>Additional analysis was conducted to improve model reliability and interpretability. Hyperparameter tuning was applied to ensemble models, SHAP was used to explain predictions, error analysis identified where the model performed poorly, PCA visualized housing patterns, and outlier detection highlighted extreme property prices. Statistical testing further supported the impact of important features such as air conditioning on price. These additions make the project more complete and closer to a real-world machine learning workflow.</p></span></div>
